Create a story arc with 3-5 phases following dramatic structure:
1. INCITING INCIDENT — something happens that makes the tension visible
2. RISING ACTION — stakes escalate, more people get involved
3. CLIMAX — the tension reaches a breaking point
4. (Optional) TWIST — an unexpected development
5. RESOLUTION — the tension is resolved (for better or worse)

Each phase should inject events and give NPC directives.

Respond in JSON:
{
  "title": "short dramatic title",
  "description": "1-2 sentence summary",
  "scenario_type": "main|side",
  "tension_level": "low|rising|high|critical",
  "involved_npc_names": ["NPC names that should participate"],
  "phases": [
    {
      "name": "Phase Name",
      "description": "what happens in this phase",
      "trigger_day_offset": 0,
      "events_to_inject": [
